<div class="wrapper clearfix">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-4 homepage_content">
            <h2 class="welcome-title">About</h2>
            <hr class="hr-text">
            <div class="about-content">
                <p>Web developer currently living in Rancho Cucamonga, California. Yes that's the city from workaholics, It's actually a real place. </p>
                <p>I&rsquo;m a 100% self taught web developer; Who is constantly learning the best practices in web development and quickly figuring out ways to apply them into my projects.</p>
                <p>My determination is what pushes me forward when I get stuck; I don&rsquo;t rely on motivation. </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4 homepage_content">
            <h2 class="welcome-title">Stuff I've Written</h2>
            <hr class="hr-text">
            <% @posts.each do |post| %>
                <h3 class="article-content"><a href="#"><%=link_to post.title, post %></a></h3>
                <p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>            
            <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4 homepage_content">
            <h2>Stuff I've Built</h2>
            <hr class="hr-text">
            <% @projects.each do |project| %>
                <h3 class="article-content"><a href="#"><%=link_to project.title, project %></a></h3>
                <p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>            
            <% end %>                          
        </div>
    </div>
</div>